WEBVTT

00:00:59.073 --> 00:01:04.080
And most importantly, commit you
to a lifetime of anticoagulation therapy.

00:01:04.104 --> 00:01:05.354
Normally, warfarin.

00:01:05.956 --> 00:01:08.570
The thought of the surgery
was not attractive.

00:01:08.594 --> 00:01:12.511
The thought of the warfarin
was really quite frightening.

00:01:13.035 --> 00:01:14.301
So I said to myself,

00:01:14.325 --> 00:01:17.756
"I'm an engineer, I'm in R&amp;D,
this is just a plumbing problem."

00:01:17.780 --> 00:01:19.786
"I can do this, I can change this."

00:01:19.810 --> 00:01:24.883
So I set out to change the entire
treatment for aortic dilation.

00:01:26.659 --> 00:01:29.459
The project aim is really quite simple.